$PAR
Evaluate the triple integral of \(f(x,y,z)=z(x^2+y^2+z^2)^{-3/2}\)
over the part of the ball \(x^2+y^2+z^2\le $r2\) defined by \( z\ge \{$r/2\}\).
$PAR
\($IIINT _{$w} f( x,y,z ) \,dV =\) \{ans_rule()\}
$PAR

